>> source: https://nutritionstudies.org/recipes/salad-dressing/strawberry-tarragon-salad-dressing/
>> serves: 3 cups
>> total time: 5 minutes

Process @strawberries{4%cups}, @shallot{1%medium}, @balsamic vinegar{1/2%cup}, @maple syrup{6%Tbsp}, @tarragon{1%Tbsp}, @pepper{1/2%tsp}, @salt{} in a #blender or food processor{} until smooth and creamy, stopping once or twice to scrape down the sides.
